<mxfile host="Electron" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) draw.io/26.0.16 Chrome/132.0.6834.196 Electron/34.2.0 Safari/537.36" version="26.0.16"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="TPu6i6wBijf45NLt5uzw"> <mxGraphModel dx="3079" dy="2517" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml

entity \"Persons\" as persons {
 + PersonID : INT
 + FirstName : VARCHAR(20)
 + LastName : VARCHAR(20)
 + Address : VARCHAR(25)
 + PhoneNumber : INT(20)
 + BirthDate : VARCHAR(26)
}

entity \"Organizations\" as organizations {
 + OrganizationID : INT
 + Name : VARCHAR(20)
 + Address : VARCHAR(20)
 + PhoneNumber : INT(20)
 + BudgetNumber : VARCHAR(20)
}

entity \"EmploymentType\" as employmentType {
 + EmploymentTypeID : INT
 + EmploymentTypeName : VARCHAR(30)
}

entity \"Employment\" as employment {
 + EmploymentID : INT
 + PersonID : INT
 + OrganizationID : INT
 + EmploymentDate : VARCHAR(20)
 + TerminationDate : VARCHAR(20)
 + Bonus : INT
 + ExtraHours : INT
}

entity \"PersonEmploymentType\" as personEmploymentType {
 + PersonEmploymentTypeID : INT
 + PersonID : INT
 + EmploymentID : INT
 + EmploymentTypeID : INT
 + StartDate : VARCHAR(22)
 + EndDate : VARCHAR(22)
}

entity \"Positions\" as positions {
 + PositionID : INT
 + Title : VARCHAR(30)
 + OrganizationID : INT
}

entity \"PersonPosition\" as personPosition {
 + PersonPositionID : INT
 + PersonID : INT
 + PositionID : INT
 + StartDate : VARCHAR(20)
 + EndDate : VARCHAR(13)
 + Salary : INT
 + EmploymentTypeID : INT
}

' Relationships
persons }|..|| employment : has
organizations }|..|| employment : employs
employmentType ||--o{ personEmploymentType : has
employment ||--o{ personEmploymentType : uses
employment }|..|| positions : occupies
organizations ||--o{ positions : offers
persons ||--o{ personPosition : holds
positions }|..|| personPosition : belongs

@enduml",
